Text: BNP Paribas Arbitrage SA grew its holdings in shares of Barnes & Noble Education by 108.5% during the 1st quarter. BNP Paribas Arbitrage SA now owns 9,317 shares of the specialty retailer's stock valued at $39,000 after purchasing an additional 4,848 shares during the last quarter.
